\id TDX - Kasua New Testament Topical Index
\mt1 Solo Keyalape Tima:na: Wekeye
\ms1 Koteyewi Timinisene Amo Seyawa Wekeye
\h 1. Puwano fa:nemi Koteyewi peleya: sosolo weyamowa a timinima:na: Kotewa kokolo kao enekeye.
\toc1 Solo Keyalape Tima:na: Wekeye
\toc2 78. Kote pukawemi kisala solowa momateyakeye.
\m Yon 1:1; Hok 1:8, 4:8
\b
\h 2. Kote Ewa kokolo kao elaposakeye.
\toc1 Solo Keyalape Tima:na: Wekeye
\toc2 78. Kote pukawemi kisala solowa momateyakeye.
\m 1 Tim 1:17; Hok 1:8
\b
\h 3. Kote Ewa hele heneya penaiyawalapulu ho:liyawalapulu elakeye.
\toc1 Solo Keyalape Tima:na: Wekeye
\toc2 78. Kote pukawemi kisala solowa momateyakeye.
\m Mak 13:26; Luk 2:9; 2 Kolini 3:18; 2 Pit 1:16; Hip 1:3; Hok 21:23
\b
\h 4. Peleya: we mei falala nano ketea sopoke Kote ene hetetima epita: heteti.
\toc1 Solo Keyalape Tima:na: Wekeye
\toc2 78. Kote pukawemi kisala solowa momateyakeye.
\m Apa 17:24-26; Efe 3:9; Kolosi 1:16; Hip 11:3; Hok 4:11
\b
\h 5. Koteyewi timinisewa hele heneye hekeya sopokeye.
\toc1 Solo Keyalape Tima:na: Wekeye
\toc2 78. Kote pukawemi kisala solowa momateyakeye.
\m 1 Pit 1:15-16; Hok 4:8, 15:3-4
\b
\h 6. Sena sale amokiwa Koteyewi mokopo seselese napola:tesekeye.
\toc1 Solo Keyalape Tima:na: Wekeye
\toc2 78. Kote pukawemi kisala solowa momateyakeye.
\m Apa 13:43; 1 Kolini 15:10; 2 Kolini 1:12; 1 Pit 5:5
\b
\h 7. Kotewa nini ni Atakeye.
\toc1 Solo Keyalape Tima:na: Wekeye
\toc2 78. Kote pukawemi kisala solowa momateyakeye.
\m Ma:t 5:45-48, 6:9,32, 7:11; Luk 6:35; Lom 8:15; Hip 12:7; 1 Pit 1:17; 1 Yon 3:1
\b
\h 8. Kote penaiyawa sosokeye.
\toc1 Solo Keyalape Tima:na: Wekeye
\toc2 78. Kote pukawemi kisala solowa momateyakeye.
\m Luk 1:37; Hok 4:8, 19:1
\b
\h 9. Koteyawa takale matanesewa sosokeye.
\toc1 Solo Keyalape Tima:na: Wekeye
\toc2 78. Kote pukawemi kisala solowa momateyakeye.
\m Lom 11:33, 16:25-27; 1 Kolini 1:25
\b
