\toc1 Solo Keyalape Tima:na: Wekeye
\toc2 78. Kote pukawemi kisala solowa momateyakeye.
\m Luk 1:50, 6:36; Efe 2:4; Tai 3:5
\b
\h 12. Koteyawa niwa himu hapa matanawa elakeye.
\toc1 Solo Keyalape Tima:na: Wekeye
\toc2 78. Kote pukawemi kisala solowa momateyakeye.
\m Yon 3:16; Lom 5:5,8; Efe 2:4-5; 1 Yon 3:1, 4:9,16
\b
\h 13. Kote Ewa hele heneye hekeyakeye.
\toc1 Solo Keyalape Tima:na: Wekeye
\toc2 78. Kote pukawemi kisala solowa momateyakeye.
