\h 65. Niyawa Yesu penaiya emi ho olokeyatela hamona e sela:pa:.
\toc1 Solo Keyalape Tima:na: Wekeye
\toc2 78. Kote pukawemi kisala solowa momateyakeye.
\m Ma:t 10:1,8; Mak 6:7,13, 9:25-29, 16:17; Luk 9:1, 10:17-20; Apa 8:7, 16:16-18, 19:11-16
